source.name: Traffic Count Sites - Map View
source.description:
This list includes Traffic Count Sites in the City of Edmonton. There are two kinds of traffic count sites:
1. Midblock site - traffic volume, direction of travel, classification (some sites), speed (Some sites)

2. Intersection site - turning direction, traffic volume, classification (some sites)
